This includes 3 files, lab1a.c, Makefile, and README.

lab1a.c - This is the C program that accepts the command line argument --shell. In default mode, it disables certain function of the terminal mode and rebuilds them. In --shell mode, it executes given shell and then the user can run commands through the shell, seeing any output echoed by their commands as well.

Makefile - This helps to build the program with options like make, make clean, and make dist.

README - This is the readme, providing info about each of the included files.

